      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_3109163195208041156.png",
                "id": "talent24787",
                "key": "线列枪刺·改",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "线列枪刺·改"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此技能结算后：</span>如果我方手牌中含有<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超量装药弹头</span>，则<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">舍弃</span>1张并治疗我方受伤最多的角色1点。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/52cd1e5b70e7ea798b5a41cd9a51fbef_7496433081687835465.png",
                "id": "talent99508",
                "key": "近迫式急促拦射",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "近迫式急促拦射"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>，在敌方场上生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">二重毁伤弹</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/a36c7a9c9512124baf0b482d8dc69912_3452447836750005441.png",
                "id": "talent29824",
                "key": "圆阵掷弹爆轰术",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "圆阵掷弹爆轰术"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">敌方角色受到超载反应伤害后：</span>生成手牌<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超量装药弹头</span>（每回合1次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/4b48c030ba601eab2fe4d2375057a617_5992848247016351617.png",
                "id": "talent29328",
                "key": "纵阵武力统筹",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "纵阵武力统筹"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">事件牌</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">战斗行动：</span>对敌方「出战角色」造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此牌被舍弃时：</span>对敌方「出战角色」造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6933733400072507195.png",
                "id": "talent26042",
                "key": "超量装药弹头",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/5dca55a012526872199ffb25f0129241_445786923583409617.png",
                "title": "超量装药弹头"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">超载</span>：本伤害+2，目标强制切换到下一个角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧</span>：本伤害+1，生成回合结束时造成1点火伤害的[<span style=\"color: white\">燃烧烈焰</span>]（可用次数1，最多叠加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_2384076818432452515.png",
                "id": "talent52280",
                "key": "火元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">二重毁伤弹</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所在阵营切换角色后：</span>对切换到的角色造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">战斗行动</span></strong></p><p>我方执行了一次战斗行动后，会轮到对方行动。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">打出具有此规则的手牌是一个战斗行动，而非快速行动。</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/17/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_203491378434643436.png",
